description: "This map's cartouche features an illustration of three men bowing before a ruler on a throne. There is also what was probably meant to be a lion, though the poor likeness suggests it was based on written descriptions rather than real life experience."
title: "Asiae recentissima delineatio, qua status et imperia totius orientis unacum orientalibus Indiis exhibentur / authore Ioh: Bapt: Homanno s.c.m. geographo."
